Today it is 296 since this torrent was created. Currently 75% is finished, which means about 37 GB (49.37  * 0.75) has been uploaded. Now, if we take those 37 gigs and divide them with the number of days this torrent has been active (296) we get that you've been seeding about 0.125 GB or 128 MB per day.  Since there are 86400 seconds (24h * 60m * 60s) per day we can quickly calculate that you are seeding with about 1.51 kB/s (128MB * 1024 / 86400) which I must say would be a new world record when it comes to slow seeding. 1.51 kB/s for heavens sake! For a 50 GB torrent!!!
